metadata.description: Silent King Society is proud to present Andy Warhol's `Superman` from 1981 as NFT. 5.000 digital pieces of this painting are out for sale. The owner of the NFT is also the owner of that specific part of the painting. The certificate of authenticity and the legal contract between us and the holder of the NFT are stored on the blockchain. The Painting is stored in a secure vault and will be sent to the collector of all 5.000 NFTs.
